latestIgtvVideos.title: DON’T GET DOGS WITHOUT GAINING KNOWLEDGE ABOUT THEM!
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Know about dogs before buying them. Understand your duties and responsibilities towards petting, consult someone you think has knowledge and discuss it with your parents. Don’t make impulsive decisions about buying pets if you repent it later, shifting houses and separation anxiety could be traumatising for them. Remember, once they are in our home they become a family and a part of our life..for the whole of their lives.🐾❤️
